```js
import <%= packageLabel %>ChartPlugin from '@bridge-ui/plugin-chart-<%= packageName %>';

new <%= packageLabel %>ChartPlugin()
  .configure({ key: '<%= packageName %>' })
  .register();
```

Then use it via `SuperChart`. See [storybook](https://apache-bridge.github.io/bridge-ui/?selectedKind=plugin-chart-<%= packageName %>) for more details.

```js
